00:40:09,130 --> 00:40:10,229
Bu Kang.

737
00:40:56,310 --> 00:40:57,750
Baiklah, Direktur Park.

738
00:40:59,149 --> 00:41:00,789
Sampai jumpa di kantor Pak Pimpinan.

739
00:41:42,229 --> 00:41:45,130
Apa? Dia menyerahkan surat pengunduran diri?

740
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:47,630
Ya, Pak Han

